Version 3.00 (08 Feb 2017)
Fixes

è	Fix: Avoid crashes on Raspberry Pi 3 (Cortex-A53) by fixing a stray "MOVS pc" instruction which had previously gone undetected.
è	Fix: Zero page access in choices handling code which would cause a crash on zero page protected OSes.
